[v0.3 changelog 18.AUG.2017]
———————————————————————————-
+ minor fixes
+ debug mode added
  (once application has started and before connecting the drone
   press Command + D this will activate debug logging.
   DZB_log.txt will be saved to your Desktop. You may send it
   to the developer if requested for troubleshooting)
   
   
